'''Em'liy''' language was the native language of the [[Em'liy/Legends|Em'liy]] [[Species/Legends|species]] from [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Shalyvane]].<ref name="Ultimate Alien Anthology" />

Most Em'liy individuals were also fluent in [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]].<ref name="Ultimate Alien Anthology" />

